    <item>
      <title>贝莱德认为科技板块不会出现轮动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/blackrock-sees-no-rotation-out-of-tech-sectors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德的乌尔苏拉·马尔基奥尼 (Ursula Marchioni) 表示，科技行业并没有出现“轮换”，而是“向金融领域扩展”。马尔基奥尼在彭博电视上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/blackrock-sees-no-rotation-out-of-tech-sectors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威调整后失业率创 19 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/norway-s-adjusted-unemployment-hits-highest-level-in-19-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威调整后的失业率上个月升至2022年以来的最高水平，超过了央行的预期，并提高了明年之前降息的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/norway-s-adjusted-unemployment-hits-highest-level-in-19-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，万国数据拟融资 10 亿美元，用于在中国境外拓展数据中心业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/gds-said-to-seek-more-funding-for-gds-international-data-centers-outside-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，万国数据控股有限公司 (GDS Holdings Ltd.) 正寻求对其在中国境外运营数据中心的子公司进行高达 10 亿美元的投资，此前该公司几个月前的一次融资获得了热烈反响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/gds-said-to-seek-more-funding-for-gds-international-data-centers-outside-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:13:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 减产导致俄罗斯石油钻探量低于纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/russia-s-oil-drilling-slips-from-record-amid-opec-output-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯进一步加大对 OPEC+ 石油产量的削减，该国石油公司的钻井速度已较去年的记录有所降低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/russia-s-oil-drilling-slips-from-record-amid-opec-output-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
